        "caption": "Decision tree based on ${7*7}. Branch a{*comment*}b -> ${'z'.join('ab')} -> Smarty / Mako. Branch {{7*7}} -> {{7*'7'}} -> Jinja2 / Twig. Otherwise, not vulnerable. Source: PayloadsAllTheThings."
